#define DIAGLIB_EMIF_START_ADDR   (0x80000000U)
 Start address of EMIF memory space. If the start address of EMIF changes, update here and rebuild.
 
#define DIAGLIB_OCMC_RAM_START_ADDR   (0x40300000U)
 Start address of OCMC memory space. If the start address of OCMC changes, update here and rebuild.
 
#define DIAGLIB_ECC_L2RAM_BYTES   (0x08U)
 Number of 8-bit data to be stored or restored for L2 RAM access.

Detailed Description

This file contains the prototypes of the APIs present in the software test library file of ECC. This also contains some related macros.
